canon_parallel  --- CUPS parallel backend for Canon Bubble Jet Printer.
canon-usb       --- CUPS USB backend for Canon Bubble Jet Printer.

DESCRIPTION
    The "canon_parallel" and "canon-usb" are the CUPS backend programs.
    which fork the "lgmon*" process to obtain the printer status.

REQUIREMENTS
    You need the following libraries.
    * libcups               (1.1.x or above)

    And you need the following programs.
    * CUPS                  (1.1.14 or above)
    * bjfilter command set. (2.4    or above)
       e.g.) bjfilterpixus560i-2.4-0.i386.rpm

      "bjfilter command set" is provided by Canon INC.

INSTALLATION
    See the file "INSTALL"

LICENSE
    See the file "LICENSE.canon.txt" which is the license terms for the
    programs made by Canon, and "LICENSE.txt" which is the original license
    terms for the usb and parallel backend programs derived from the code
    made by Easy Software Products.

